text: Ra hamile bani isra'ilala'i samudrabata para garayaum. Ani tiniharu yasta manisaharuka samipama puge junaki aphna kehi devataharu che'u baseka thi'e, bhannathaleh ‘‘he musa! Hamro nimti pani yastai e'uta devata niyukta garidinus jasto ki yiniharuka yi devataharu chan’’. Unale bhane ki samccai nai timiharuma thulo ajnanata cha
